UDFs.name: spc_get_hc_rt_bsa_fnc
UDFs.functionBody:
declare 

    v_vop_cd        varchar(3);
    v_hc_rt         real := 0; 
    V_OWN_CRR_CD    varchar(10) := 'ONE';
  

BEGIN
    
    SELECT --DECODE(CRR_CD, V_OWN_CRR_CD, CRR_CD, 'OTH') AS V_VOP_CD 
        (CASE WHEN CRR_CD = V_OWN_CRR_CD THEN CRR_CD
            ELSE 'OTH' END) AS V_VOP_CD
        INTO v_vop_cd 
    FROM MDM_VSL_CNTR 
    WHERE 1=1 
        AND VSL_CD = in_vsl_cd 
        AND DELT_FLG = 'N' 
    ;

    SELECT
      CASE 
      WHEN coalesce(DTL.HC_RT,2) < 1 
      THEN 2 
      ELSE coalesce(DTL.HC_RT,2) 
       END AS V_HC_RT 
      INTO STRICT v_hc_rt 
      FROM BSA_HIGH_CUBIC_RT_MST MST 
         INNER JOIN BSA_HIGH_CUBIC_RT_DTL DTL
            ON (MST.CNTR_TPSZ_CD = DTL.CNTR_TPSZ_CD
                AND MST.BSA_SEQ = DTL.BSA_SEQ)
         INNER JOIN( 
              SELECT  TO_CHAR(N1ST_LODG_PORT_ETD_DT,'YYYYMMDD') AS EFF_DT 
              FROM COA_MON_VVD 
              WHERE 1=1 
               AND VSL_CD  = in_vsl_cd 
               AND SKD_VOY_NO = in_skd_voy_no 
               AND DIR_CD =  in_dir_cd 
               AND TRD_CD = in_trd_cd 
               AND RLANE_CD = in_rlan_cd 
               AND DELT_FLG = 'N' 
         ) CMV 
            ON (CMV.EFF_DT BETWEEN MST.BSA_FM_DT AND MST.BSA_TO_DT)
     WHERE 1=1 
       AND MST.CNTR_TPSZ_CD = in_hc_tp_cd 
       AND MST.TRD_CD = in_trd_cd 
       AND MST.RLANE_CD = in_rlan_cd 
       AND MST.DIR_CD = in_dir_cd 
       AND MST.VOP_CD = v_vop_cd 
       AND MST.DELT_FLG = 'N' 
       AND DTL.CRR_CD = V_OWN_CRR_CD
       LIMIT 1
    ; 

  RETURN v_hc_rt ;
  
  EXCEPTION
      WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND
      THEN
         BEGIN
            SELECT CNTR_SZ_TEU_CAPA INTO STRICT v_hc_rt FROM MDM_CNTR_SZ WHERE CNTR_SZ_CD = substring(in_hc_tp_cd, 2,1) LIMIT 1;
            RETURN v_hc_rt;
         EXCEPTION
            WHEN NO_DATA_FOUND
             THEN
              BEGIN
                v_hc_rt := 2 ;
                RETURN v_hc_rt;
              END;
     END;

END 
;

UDFs.name: globaldate_pkg_time_conv_ofc_fnc
UDFs.functionBody:
/**
    * 
     * Ex) SELECT GLOBALDATE_PKG_TIME_CONV_OFC_FNC('KRPUS', TO_TIMESTAMP('202102011521', 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS'), 'USCHI');
     */
    BEGIN
        RETURN (SELECT (CASE WHEN (UPPER(v_fr_ofc_cd) = 'GMT' AND UPPER(v_to_ofc_cd) != 'GMT')
                               THEN (SELECT (v_fr_loc_time + CONCAT(COALESCE((
						SELECT	A.GMT_HRS
						FROM	MDM_LOCATION A,
						            MDM_ORGANIZATION B
						WHERE	B.OFC_CD=v_to_ofc_cd
						AND	B.DELT_FLG='N'
						AND	A.LOC_CD=B.LOC_CD
                                                                          ), 0
                                                                 ),
                                                                 ' MINUTES'
                                                          )::INTERVAL
                                                        + CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT B.DST_MNTS DST_MINS
                                                                             FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                  MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                 								  MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                            WHERE C.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                              AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                              AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                              AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                              AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD IS NULL
                                                                              AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= (SELECT v_fr_loc_time + CONCAT(COALESCE(GMT_HRS, 0), ' MINUTES')::INTERVAL
                                                                                                    FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                                                   WHERE B.OFC_CD=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                                   AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                   AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                                                 )
                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= (SELECT v_fr_loc_time + CONCAT(COALESCE(GMT_HRS, 0), ' MINUTES')::INTERVAL
                                                                                                    FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                                                   WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                                   AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                   AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                                                  )
                                                                              AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT	B.*
                                                                                               FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                                       MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                                       MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                                              WHERE C.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                                AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                                                AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                                                AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                                                AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD = A.STE_CD
                                                                                                AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= (SELECT v_fr_loc_time + CONCAT(COALESCE(GMT_HRS, 0), ' MINUTES')::INTERVAL
                                                                                                                      FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                                                                     WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                                                      AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                                      AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                                                                   )
                                                                                                AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= (SELECT v_fr_loc_time + CONCAT(COALESCE(GMT_HRS, 0), ' MINUTES')::INTERVAL
                                                                                                                       FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                                                                      WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                                                      AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                                      AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                                                                    )
                                                                                  )
                                                                          ), 0
                                                                 ),
                                                                 ' MINUTES'
                                                          )::INTERVAL
                                            )
                                    )
                             WHEN ( UPPER(v_fr_ofc_cd) != 'GMT' AND UPPER(v_to_ofc_cd) = 'GMT')
                               THEN (SELECT (v_fr_loc_time - CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT B.DST_MNTS
                                                                             FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                  MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                  MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                            WHERE  C.OFC_CD	=v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                              AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                              AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                              AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                              AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD IS	NULL
                                                                              AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                              AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT B.*
                                                                                               FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                                    MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B
                                                                                              WHERE A.LOC_CD = v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                                AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                                                AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD = A.STE_CD
                                                                                                AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                                AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                      )
                                                                          ), 0
                                                                 ),
                                                                 ' MINUTES'
                                                          )::INTERVAL
                                                        - CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT GMT_HRS
                                                                             FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                            WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                   AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                   AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                          ), 0
                                                                 ),
                                                                 ' MINUTES'
                                                          )::INTERVAL
                                            )
                                    )
                            WHEN ( UPPER(v_fr_ofc_cd) = 'GMT' AND UPPER(v_to_ofc_cd) = 'GMT')
                               THEN (SELECT v_fr_loc_time)
                             /**
                              * FROM LOCAL TIME - FROM LOCAL DST - GMT+
                              * +
                              * TO GMT+ + TO LOCAL DST
                              */
                             ELSE (SELECT (v_fr_loc_time - CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT B.DST_MNTS DST_MINS
                                                                           FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                          WHERE C.OFC_CD	=v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                              AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                              AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                            AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                            AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD IS NULL
                                                                            AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                            AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                            AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                            AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT B.*
                                                                                             FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                                  MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                                  MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                                            WHERE  C.OFC_CD = v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                              AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                                              AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                                              AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                                              AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD = A.STE_CD
                                                                                              AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                    )
                                                                        ), 0
                                                               ),
                                                               ' MINUTES'
                                                        )::INTERVAL
                                                      - CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT GMT_HRS
                                                                           FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                          WHERE B.OFC_CD	= v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                   AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                   AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                        ), 0
                                                               ),
                                                               ' MINUTES'
                                                        )::INTERVAL
                                                      + CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT GMT_HRS
                                                                           FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                          WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                   AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                   AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                        ), 0
                                                               ),
                                                               ' MINUTES'
                                                        )::INTERVAL
                                                      + CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT B.DST_MNTS DST_MINS
                                                                           FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                MDM_ORGANIZATION D,
                                                                                (SELECT (v_fr_loc_time - CONCAT(COALESCE((SELECT B.DST_MNTS DST_MINS
                                                                                                                         FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                                                              MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                            MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                                                                        WHERE C.OFC_CD	= v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                                                           AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                                                                           AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                                                                          AND A.CNT_CD =	B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                                                                          AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD IS	NULL
                                                                                                                          AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                                          AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                                                          AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                                                          AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT B.*
                                                                                                                                           FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                                                                                MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                                              MDM_ORGANIZATION C
                                                                                                                                          WHERE C.OFC_CD	=v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                                                                            AND C.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                                                                                            AND A.LOC_CD = C.LOC_CD
                                                                                                                                            AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                                                                                            AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD = A.STE_CD
                                                                                                                                            AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                                                            AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                                                                            AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= v_fr_loc_time
                                                                                                                              )
                                                                                                                      ), 0
                                                                                                             ),
                                                                                                             ' MINUTES'
                                                                                                      )::INTERVAL
                                                                                                    - CONCAT((SELECT GMT_HRS
                                                                                                                FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                                                                WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_fr_ofc_cd
                                                                                                                AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                                AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                                                             ),
                                                                                                             ' MINUTES'
                                                                                                      )::INTERVAL
                                                                                                    + CONCAT((SELECT GMT_HRS
                                                                                                                FROM MDM_LOCATION A, MDM_ORGANIZATION B
                                                                                                                WHERE B.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                                                AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                                                AND A.LOC_CD   = B.LOC_CD
                                                                                                             ),
                                                                                                             ' MINUTES'
                                                                                                      )::INTERVAL
                                                                                        ) v_to_loc_time
                                                                                ) C
                                                                          WHERE  D.OFC_CD	=v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                            AND D.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                            AND A.LOC_CD = D.LOC_CD
                                                                            AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                            AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD IS NULL
                                                                            AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                            AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= C.v_to_loc_time
                                                                            AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= C.v_to_loc_time
                                                                            AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT B.*
                                                                                             FROM MDM_LOCATION A,
                                                                                                  MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM B,
				                                                                                  MDM_ORGANIZATION X
                                                                                            WHERE X.OFC_CD	= v_to_ofc_cd
                                                                                              AND X.DELT_FLG	='N'
                                                                                              AND A.LOC_CD = X.LOC_CD
                                                                                              AND A.CNT_CD = B.DST_CNT_CD
                                                                                              AND B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD = A.STE_CD
                                                                                              AND B.DELT_FLG = 'N'
                                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= C.v_to_loc_time
                                                                                              AND TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= C.v_to_loc_time
                                                                                )
                                                                        ), 0
                                                               ),
                                                               ' MINUTES'
                                                        )::INTERVAL
                                          )
                                  )
                        END
                       )
               )
        ;
    END

UDFs.functionBody:
declare
	po_rtn_value  VARCHAR(50) := '';

BEGIN
	SELECT    CASE WHEN (
                            SELECT  COUNT(1) 
                            FROM    VSK_VSL_SKD             VS 
                            WHERE   VS.VSL_CD               = PS.VSL_CD 
                            AND     VS.SKD_VOY_NO           = PS.SKD_VOY_NO
                            AND     VS.SKD_DIR_CD           = PS.SKD_DIR_CD                            
                            AND     EXISTS                  (SELECT ''
                                                             FROM   VSK_VSL_SKD             X1
                                                             WHERE  X1.VSL_SLAN_CD          = VS.VSL_SLAN_CD
                                                             AND    X1.VSL_CD               = VS.VSL_CD
                                                             AND    X1.SKD_VOY_NO           = VS.SKD_VOY_NO
                                                             AND    X1.SKD_DIR_CD           = VS.SKD_DIR_CD
                                                             AND    X1.VSL_NM_XTER_HIDE_FLG = 'Y'
                                                             )
                            
                            ) > 0 THEN 'To Be Nominated' 
                       WHEN pi_cssm_voy_kind_cd = 'I' THEN concat(VC.VSL_ENG_NM,' ',coalesce(PS.IB_CSSM_VOY_NO,PS.SKD_VOY_NO||PS.SKD_DIR_CD))
                       WHEN pi_cssm_voy_kind_cd = 'O' THEN concat(VC.VSL_ENG_NM,' ',coalesce(PS.OB_CSSM_VOY_NO,PS.SKD_VOY_NO||PS.SKD_DIR_CD)) 
              END          
    INTO      po_rtn_value
    FROM      MDM_VSL_CNTR        VC 
           ,  VSK_VSL_SKD         VS
           ,  VSK_VSL_PORT_SKD    PS  
    WHERE     1 = 1
    AND       VC.VSL_CD           = PS.VSL_CD
    AND       VS.VSL_CD           = PS.VSL_CD
    AND       VS.SKD_VOY_NO       = PS.SKD_VOY_NO
    AND       VS.SKD_DIR_CD       = PS.SKD_DIR_CD
    AND       PS.VSL_CD           = pi_vsl_cd
    AND       PS.SKD_VOY_NO       = pi_skd_voy_no
    AND       PS.SKD_DIR_CD       = pi_skd_dir_cd     
    AND       PS.VPS_PORT_CD      = pi_port_cd
    AND       PS.CLPT_IND_SEQ     = pi_clpt_ind_seq        
    ;
            
    RETURN po_rtn_value;

EXCEPTION
    WHEN OTHERS THEN
    RAISE;

    RETURN NULL;
	

END;

UDFs.name: bkg_get_vgm_cut_tm_fnc
UDFs.functionBody:
declare 

  r_dct      DATE   ;

BEGIN

  SELECT odsadm.BKG_GET_VGM_CCT_FNC(SKD.POL_NOD_CD,
                           SKD.SLAN_CD,
                           SKD.SLAN_DIR_CD,
                           SKD.CGO_TP_CD,
                           SKD.VVD,
                           SKD.CLPT_IND_SEQ,
                           (SKD.VPS_ETB_DT)::date,
                           (SKD.VPS_ETD_DT)::date) AS VGM_CCT
  INTO r_dct
  FROM (SELECT SKD.SLAN_CD SLAN_CD
               ,VVD.SKD_DIR_CD SLAN_DIR_CD
               ,CASE WHEN DCGO_FLG = 'Y' THEN 'DG'
                     WHEN RC_FLG = 'Y' THEN 'RF'
                     WHEN DCGO_FLG = 'N' AND RC_FLG = 'N' AND AWK_CGO_FLG = 'N' AND BB_CGO_FLG = 'N' THEN 'DR'
                ELSE 'AL'
               END CGO_TP_CD
              ,VPS_ETB_DT
              ,VPS_ETD_DT
              ,POL_NOD_CD
              ,coalesce(VVD.POL_CLPT_IND_SEQ, '1') AS CLPT_IND_SEQ
              ,concat(VVD.VSL_CD, VVD.SKD_VOY_NO, VVD.SKD_DIR_CD) AS VVD
         FROM BKG_BOOKING BK, BKG_VVD VVD, VSK_VSL_PORT_SKD SKD
         WHERE BK.BKG_NO = VVD.BKG_NO
           AND BK.POL_CD = VVD.POL_CD
           AND VVD.VSL_PRE_PST_CD IN ('S', 'T')
           AND VVD.VSL_CD NOT IN ('COXX', 'COYY', 'COZZ')
           AND VVD.VSL_CD = SKD.VSL_CD
           AND VVD.SKD_VOY_NO = SKD.SKD_VOY_NO
           AND VVD.SKD_DIR_CD = SKD.SKD_DIR_CD
           AND VVD.POL_CD = SKD.VPS_PORT_CD
           AND coalesce(VVD.POL_CLPT_IND_SEQ, '1') = SKD.CLPT_IND_SEQ
           AND BK.BKG_NO = v_bkg_no
           ORDER BY VVD.VSL_PRE_PST_CD,VSL_SEQ
          ) SKD
  limit 1          
  ;

  RETURN  r_dct ;


  EXCEPTION
  WHEN  NO_DATA_FOUND THEN
      RETURN  NULL ;


END 
;

globaldate_pkg_time_local_ofc_fnc
UDFs.functionBody:
declare OUT_DATE TIMESTAMP;
declare v_cnt_cd VARCHAR(2); --현재 실행되는 Server의 국가 식별
declare v_db_tmz integer;

    /**
     * Location Code를 이용해서 지역 시간 검색 함수
     * 
     * Ex) SELECT GLOBALDATE_PKG_TIME_LOCAL_OFC_FNC('USCHI');
     */
    BEGIN
    
        v_cnt_cd = 'KR';
    		/*SELECT	CASE
					WHEN SUBSTR(GLOBAL_NAME, 1, 6) = 'HJSDOM' THEN 'US' --CST5CDT
					ELSE 'KR'
				  END
		     INTO v_cnt_cd
		     FROM GLOBAL_NAME*/
		
		    v_db_tmz := EXTRACT(TIMEZONE_HOUR FROM CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) * 60 + EXTRACT(TIMEZONE_MINUTE FROM CURRENT_TIMESTAMP);
		    
		  SELECT	(
					/**************************************************
						Server SYSDATE - Server LOCAL DST - Server GMT
						+ TO GMT + TO LOCAL DST
					**************************************************/
					SELECT
								CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
  							- CONCAT(COALESCE
          								(
          									(
          										SELECT	B.DST_MNTS DST_MNTS
          										FROM	MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM	B
          										WHERE	B.DST_CNT_CD					=	v_cnt_cd --KRSEL OR USCHI
          										AND		B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD			IS	NULL --Country 전체 State에 기본적으로 적용되는 값
          										AND		B.DELT_FLG						=	'N'
                              AND   TO_TIMESTAMP(B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') <= CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
                              AND   TO_TIMESTAMP(B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT,'YYYYMMDDHH24MI') >= CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
          									), 0
                           ), ' MINUTES'
                    )::INTERVAL
								- CONCAT( CASE WHEN v_cnt_cd = 'US' THEN  -360 ELSE v_db_tmz END , ' MINUTES' )::INTERVAL
  							+ CONCAT(COALESCE
          								(
          									(
            									SELECT  A.GMT_HRS
            									  FROM	MDM_LOCATION A,
            										      MDM_ORGANIZATION	B
            									 WHERE	B.OFC_CD	=	v_to_ofc_cd
            									   AND	B.DELT_FLG	=	'N'
            								     AND	A.LOC_CD	=	B.LOC_CD
          									), 0
                           ), ' MINUTES'
                    )::INTERVAL
  							+ CONCAT(COALESCE
          								(
          									(
        										SELECT	B.DST_MNTS DST_MNTS
        										FROM	MDM_LOCATION		A,
        												MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM	B,
        												MDM_ORGANIZATION	D,
        												(
        													SELECT	(
        																CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
        																- CONCAT( CASE WHEN v_cnt_cd = 'US' THEN  -360 ELSE v_db_tmz END , ' MINUTES' )::INTERVAL
        																+  CONCAT(COALESCE
									          								(
									          									(
              																	SELECT	A.GMT_HRS
              																	FROM	MDM_LOCATION		A,
              																			MDM_ORGANIZATION	B
              																	WHERE	B.OFC_CD	=	v_to_ofc_cd
              																	AND		B.DELT_FLG	=	'N'
              																	AND		A.LOC_CD	=	B.LOC_CD
      												                				), 0
													                           ), ' MINUTES'
													                    )::INTERVAL
	        														) v_to_loc_time
    	   												)	C
        											WHERE	D.OFC_CD						=	v_to_ofc_cd
        											AND		D.DELT_FLG						=	'N'
        											AND		A.LOC_CD						=	D.LOC_CD
        											AND		A.CNT_CD						=	B.DST_CNT_CD
        											AND		B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD			IS	NULL --Country 전체 State에 기본적으로 적용되는 값
        											AND		B.DELT_FLG						=	'N'
        											AND		B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT		<=	TO_CHAR(C.v_to_loc_time, 'RRRRMMDDHH24MI')
        											AND		B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT	>=	TO_CHAR(C.v_to_loc_time, 'RRRRMMDDHH24MI')
        											AND		NOT EXISTS	(
        																	SELECT	B.*
        																	FROM	MDM_LOCATION		A,
        																			MDM_DYLGT_SAV_TM	B,
        																			MDM_ORGANIZATION	D
        																	WHERE	D.OFC_CD						=	v_to_ofc_cd
        																	AND		D.DELT_FLG						=	'N'
        																	AND		A.LOC_CD						=	D.LOC_CD
        																	AND		A.CNT_CD						=	B.DST_CNT_CD
        																	AND		B.DST_NOT_APLY_STE_CD			=	A.STE_CD
        																	AND		B.DELT_FLG						=	'N'
        																	AND		B.ST_DST_DT||B.ST_DST_HRMNT		<=	TO_CHAR(C.v_to_loc_time, 'RRRRMMDDHH24MI')
        																	AND		B.END_DST_DT||B.END_DST_HRMNT	>=	TO_CHAR(C.v_to_loc_time, 'RRRRMMDDHH24MI')
        																)
          									), 0
                           ), ' MINUTES'
                    )::INTERVAL 
				)
		INTO OUT_DATE;				
        
  RETURN OUT_DATE;
        
END

begin

	return query
    select   row_number() OVER () SEQ

			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,4) col_4

			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,9) col_9
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,10) col_10
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,11) col_11
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,12) col_12
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,13) col_13
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,14) col_14
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,15) col_15
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,16) col_16
			,split_part(ALIAS.value,v_col_split,17) col_17
